        <item>
            <title>【MWC2025】Anker Solix Cloak 太陽能充電斗篷，外形似足 Jedi、30W USB-C 輸出</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/03/04/anker-solix/fun-tech/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=anker-solix</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/03/04/anker-solix/fun-tech/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Tue, 04 Mar 2025 09:22:58 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[科技新聞]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Anker]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[ANKER Cloak]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[MWC2025]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1295239</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>ANKER 在西班牙舉行的流動通訊展 MWC 2025 展示了一款太陽能充電概念外套 ANKER Solix Cloak，外套配備太陽能板，可為手機充電，外觀設計酷似《星球大戰》的絕地武士服裝。這款外套以鈣鈦礦材料製成太陽能電池，並設有 30W USB-C 輸出線，方便連接裝置充電。產品目前仍屬概念階段，未知何時正式推出市場。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1295498" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/472888929_5715948658-580x580.jpg" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/472888929_5715948658-580x580.jpg 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/472888929_5715948658.jpg 900w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/472888929_5715948658-144x144.jpg 144w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1295499" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/ggvc86_xsaaavkl-694x462.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/ggvc86_xsaaavkl-694x462.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/ggvc86_xsaaavkl-scaled.jpeg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1295243" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/ankersolixcloak_rede-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/ankersolixcloak_rede-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/ankersolixcloak_rede.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>ANKER Solix 這款名為「Cloak（斗篷）」的太陽能外套，表面縫有 24 塊鈣鈦礦太陽能電池，質感似布料且具一定柔韌性。外套設有 30W USB-C 輸出，可接駁行動電源或直接為電子產品充電，適合户外活動時使用。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1295244" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/ankersolixcloak_rede-1-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/ankersolixcloak_rede-1-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/ankersolixcloak_rede-1.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1295245" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/ankersolixcloak_rede-2-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/ankersolixcloak_rede-2-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/ankersolixcloak_rede-2.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>外套設計上加入藍色 LED 光條點綴帽邊，提升夜間能見度兼具未來感，猶如科幻電影中的服裝。外套外形似雨衣，輕巧並配有拉鍊，太陽能板分佈於前胸、後背及右臂，右臂部分特別採用三角形設計，方便活動。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1295246" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/ankersolixcloak_rede-3-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/ankersolixcloak_rede-3-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/ankersolixcloak_rede-3.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1295248" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/ankersolixcloak_rede-5-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/ankersolixcloak_rede-5-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/ankersolixcloak_rede-5.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1295251" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/screenshot20250302at-694x390.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/screenshot20250302at-694x390.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/screenshot20250302at.jpeg 1200w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲圖片來源：CNET</p><p>據 CNET 報道，ANKER Solix 早前於 CES 2025 已展示其他太陽能產品，如即將推出的 EverFrost 2 冷卻器及夏季發售的太陽能傘，顯示其積極拓展太陽能應用領域。ANKER Solix 近年專注開發創新能源解決方案，除外套外，其太陽能傘及便攜電源 SOLIX C200 亦備受矚目，反映太陽能技術正逐步融入日常生活。業界人士預計，鈣鈦礦太陽能電池因成本低、效能高，未來或廣泛應用於穿戴裝置及户外用品。ANKER Solix 的太陽能外套於 Mobile World Congress 2025 亮相，以創新設計及實用功能吸引目光。雖然尚處概念階段，但預料相關產品有望加速開發。</p><div class="epyt-video-wrapper"><iframe loading="lazy"  style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;"  id="_ytid_56033"  width="590" height="332"  data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/-lId9_re3uc?enablejsapi=1&#038;autoplay=0&#038;cc_load_policy=0&#038;cc_lang_pref=&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;loop=0&#038;modestbranding=1&#038;rel=0&#038;fs=1&#038;playsinline=1&#038;autohide=1&#038;theme=light&#038;color=white&#038;controls=1&#038;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player"  allow="fullscreen; accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></div><p>資料來源：<a href="https://www.cnet.com/tech/mobile/this-jacket-charges-your-phone-with-solar-energy-and-makes-you-look-like-a-jedi/">CNET</a></p><p>======</p><p>加入 <a href="https://www.threads.net/@unwirehk" target="_blank" rel="noopener">unwire thread</a> 傾傾科技背後黑暗事</p><p>========</p><br /><b>
]]>
            </description>
