        <item>
            <title>【MWC2025】Lenovo AI Stick 外置 AI 加速配件，配備 32 TOPS NPU，一插即加速電腦 AI 運算能力</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/03/04/lenovo-ai-stick/ai/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=lenovo-ai-stick</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/03/04/lenovo-ai-stick/ai/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Lawton]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Tue, 04 Mar 2025 08:49:01 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[人工智能]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Lenovo AI Stick]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[MWC2025]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1295457</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>時下電腦都要講 AI 處理能力，而一些用户希望為現有電腦提高 AI 處理能力，就可留意這件新產品。Lenovo 於世界流動通訊大會 MWC 2025 展示了一款全新「Lenovo AI Stick」，這款 USB-C 連接裝置內置 32 TOPS NPU，專為提供 AI 加速運算而設計。今次我們就有記者到巴塞羅那看到這款新裝置的真身。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1295458" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_20250303_092652-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_20250303_092652-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_20250303_092652-scaled.jpg 1200w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>雖然 Lenovo AI Stick 目前仍屬於概念產品，但其設計理念清晰，就是為現有電腦提供 AI 運算能力，特別是針對未內建 NPU 的系統，透過簡單插入 USB-C 連接埠，即可運行 AI 模型及圖像處理應用程式。</p><p>Lenovo 並未透露 AI Stick 內置 NPU 的供應商，但其官方資料顯示，這款設備主要用於本地運行大型語言模型（LLM）及 AI 圖像處理應用。AI Stick 兼容 Lenovo 自家的 AI Now 軟件套件，該軟件須在 Windows 11 及 x86 架構處理器上運行。裝置透過 USB-C Thunderbolt 介面連接電腦，並具備側面電源插口，若使用外部電源供應，NPU 運行速度可進一步提升，這也引發了外界對其 USB-C 供電效能的疑問。</p><p>除了增強 AI 運算能力，Lenovo 亦指出 AI Stick 可減少 GPU 佔用，降低系統温度，對於已內建 NPU 或獨立顯示卡的設備來説，仍具備一定價值。這款設備的出現，為現有電腦提供了一種升級 AI 運算的便捷方案，尤其適合處理器性能強勁但缺乏 NPU 的裝置，例如 Intel 即將推出的 Arrow Lake 平台。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1295459" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_20250303_092634-694x563.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="563" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_20250303_092634-694x563.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_20250303_092634.jpg 1110w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><br /><b>
]]>
            </description>
            <wfw:commentRss>https://unwire.hk/2025/03/04/lenovo-ai-stick/ai/feed/</wfw:commentRss>
            <slash:comments>0</slash:comments>
        </item>
        <item>
            <title>【MWC2025】Samsung S25 Edge 實物現身，多角度觀賞超薄手機</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/03/04/samsung-s25-edge/mobile-phone/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=samsung-s25-edge</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/03/04/samsung-s25-edge/mobile-phone/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Lawton]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Tue, 04 Mar 2025 08:40:40 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[手提電話]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[MWC2025]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[s25 edge]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[samsung]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1295398</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>Samsung 今年都有參加世界流動通訊展 MWC 2025，在會場中向公眾展示 Samsung Galaxy S25 Edge 實物而且沒有放在玻璃相內，另外利用 Android 平台、混合擴增實鏡 AR 與虛擬實境的 Samsung Android XR 都有在會場展示。等我們 unwire 記者到巴塞羅那會場現場同大家睇睇。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1295404" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_20250303_093649-672x580.jpg" alt="" width="672" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_20250303_093649-672x580.jpg 672w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_20250303_093649-scaled.jpg 1043w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 672px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1295399" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_20250303_110147-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_20250303_110147-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_20250303_110147.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>Samsung Project Moohan XR 是三星與 Google 合作開發的產品，預計將於明年正式推出。Project Moohan 是首款採用 Android XR 平台，的裝置， Android 將透過這個平台在，擴增實境 (AR) 和虛擬實境 (VR) 領域，進一步發展，平台未來將適用於 XR 頭戴裝置及智能眼鏡。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1295400" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_20250303_110151-694x449.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="449" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_20250303_110151-694x449.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_20250303_110151.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>Project Moohan 為全罩式頭戴裝置，外形設計類似 Apple Vision Pro。其名稱「Moohan」源自韓文，意指「無限」，象徵該裝置提供廣闊視野及高品質顯示效果，以帶來更沉浸式體驗。使用者可透過 Google Maps 進行空間導航，觀看，擴展視角的體育賽事，甚至利用 Gemini AI 助理規劃旅行行程。</p><p>而更受現場觀眾關注的是 Samsung Galaxy S25 Edge。Galaxy S25 Edge 擁有超纖薄機身，為 S 系列歷來最薄旗艦機款。三星在機身設計上採用更緊湊的內部結構，並透過改良散熱技術及材料，確保裝置在維持纖薄外型的同時，仍能提供強勁效能。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter wp-image-1295401" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_20250303_093712-428x580.jpg" alt="" width="555" height="752" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_20250303_093712-428x580.jpg 428w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_20250303_093712-scaled.jpg 664w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 555px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter wp-image-1295402" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_20250303_093723-360x580.jpg" alt="" width="555" height="894" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_20250303_093723-360x580.jpg 360w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_20250303_093723-scaled.jpg 559w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 555px" /></p><p>裝置搭載全新「Edge Display」，邊框更窄，螢幕邊緣曲線過渡更流暢，提升顯示區域的視覺延伸感。三星也進一步強化 Dynamic AMOLED 2X 面板，提升色彩準確度與對比度，並支援 LTPO 技術，帶來更流暢的自適應更新率，確保高效能與省電表現兼顧。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1295403" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_20250303_093735-694x523.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="523" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_20250303_093735-694x523.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_20250303_093735-scaled.jpg 1195w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><br /><b>
]]>
            </description>
