            <title>德勤 IT 經理偷 399 部手提電腦，2 年竊走電腦總值近 280 萬元</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/03/04/deloitte-it-manager-stole-399-computer/tech-secure/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=deloitte-it-manager-stole-399-computer</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/03/04/deloitte-it-manager-stole-399-computer/tech-secure/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Tue, 04 Mar 2025 07:22:40 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[資訊保安]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[德勤]]>
            </category>
